OL,3,CMcArthur 'confident' ahead of key vote
OL,4,Con assisted dying bill at Holyrood
OL,6,FThe MSP leading efforts to introduce
OL,7,Fassisted dying in Scotland has said he
OL,8,Fis "confident" of winning a key vote
OL,9,Fat Holyrood
OL,11,FLiberal Democrat Liam McArthur has
OL,12,Fbrought forward a member's Bill which,
OL,13,Fif passed, would allow terminally ill
OL,14,FScots to seek help to end their life.
OL,16,FWith the first vote on the Bill `
OL,17,Fwhere MSPs decide on whether or not
OL,18,Fthey support the general principles of
OL,19,Fthe legislation ` due on Tuesday, Mr
OL,20,FMcArthur said he is "confident that
OL,21,Fthe support is there".
