OL,3,CMcArthur 'confident' ahead of key vote
OL,4,Con assisted dying bill at Holyrood
OL,6,FSpeaking to the PA news agency, Mr
OL,7,FMcArthur said: "I think the general
OL,8,Fmood is while it will be close, I am
OL,9,Fconfident the support is there to
OL,10,Fallow us to go through to the next
OL,11,Fstage."
OL,13,FIt will be the third time Holyrood has
OL,14,Fvoted on the issue, with previous
OL,15,Fattempts to change the law defeated in
OL,16,Fboth 2010 and 2015.
