OL,6,FScotland's First Minister John Swinney
OL,7,Fhas said that the proposals from Mr
OL,8,FMcArthur are a "much better Bill" than
OL,9,Fthose introduced previously ` though
OL,10,Fhe stressed that he could not support
OL,11,Fthe legislation.
OL,13,FIt will however be a free vote when
OL,14,FMSPs decide on the issue on Tuesday
OL,15,Fevening.
