OL,6,FHe said Westminster MPs had initially
OL,7,Fpassed Kim Leadbeater's Bill on
OL,8,Fassisted dying to "enable the detailed
OL,9,Fcommittee scrutiny of amendments to
OL,10,Ftake place".
OL,12,FAnd he said that at Holyrood "I think
OL,13,Fwe need to go through that process
OL,14,Ftoo", adding that it "may well be that
OL,15,Famendments are brought forward that
OL,16,Fcan help address concerns".
