OL,6,FBut the Liberal Democrat, who has been
OL,7,Fworking on the issue since 2021,
OL,8,Fstated: "We only get to find that out
OL,9,Fif we pass the general principles next
OL,10,Fweek."
OL,12,FOpponents of the legislation argue
OL,13,Fthat if it is passed, it could leave
OL,14,Fvulnerable people feeling pressurised
OL,15,Fto prematurely end their life.
OL,17,FMr McArthur, however, believes that
OL,18,Fthe "political mood" at Holyrood is
OL,19,F"very, very different from what it
OL,20,Fwas" when the previous Bills were
OL,21,Fconsidered.
