OL,6,F"I think on balance 18 is a more
OL,7,Fappropriate threshold," he said.
OL,9,F"On this issue it had become
OL,10,Fincreasingly clear to me setting the
OL,11,Fage threshold at 18 would give more
OL,12,Freassurance to my MSP colleagues,
OL,13,Fincluding many who are very supportive
OL,14,Fof a change in the law."
OL,16,FHowever, he insisted that assisted
OL,17,Fdying could "provide additional choice
OL,18,Fto the small but not insignificant
OL,19,Fnumber of people for whom that is a
